00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:39,920
No!

169
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,381
No...

170
00:16:44,280 --> 00:16:45,160
No!

171
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,800
Give me back my necklace.

172
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,328
No...

173
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:53,920
Don't take it away.

174
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,360
Give it back to me.

175
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,360
Khunkhao!

176
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:02,360
Hey!

177
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:04,280
What happened?

178
00:17:04,943 --> 00:17:05,750
Khunkhao?

179
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:06,840
Khunkhao...

180
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:09,280
- Dad...
- Yeah?

181
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:11,400
My necklace...

182
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,000
My necklace...

183
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:21,520
Aisoon.

184
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:24,800
Kate.

185
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,640
Take Khunkhao to the hospital.

186
00:17:27,800 --> 00:17:28,844
Singkhon,

187
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:29,800
where are you going?

188
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:31,720
I'll go get the necklace back.

189
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:40,080
Watch out!

190
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:51,440
Singkhon!!

191
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:54,320
Dad!

192
00:17:58,843 --> 00:18:00,080
Dad...

193
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,160
Dad!

194
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:32,560
Khunkhao.

195
00:18:35,340 --> 00:18:36,520
I dreamed of my dad.

196
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:39,120
It was just a dream.

197
00:18:51,020 --> 00:18:53,280
If I had protected the Shiva lingam necklace,

198
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:57,260
my dad wouldn't have had to die.

199
00:19:01,160 --> 00:19:02,760
It's my fault...

200
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,840
that he died.

201
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:33,720
I want to know what exactly happened.

202
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:35,720
There's someone who knows that very well.

203
00:19:35,940 --> 00:19:37,120
Come closer and you'll die.

204
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:39,840
Aunt Kate!

205
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:40,720
Kill him.

206
00:19:41,733 --> 00:19:46,093
♫No matter how long it takes♫

207
00:19:46,133 --> 00:19:48,733
♫I'll still choose to love you♫

208
00:20:09,373 --> 00:20:10,373
Singkhon...

209
00:20:15,033 --> 00:20:16,213
I'm sorry.

210
00:20:19,813 --> 00:20:22,333
I really didn't know
what to do at the time.

211
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:44,723
Are you crying?

212
00:20:48,533 --> 00:20:49,533
Is everything okay?

213
00:20:53,333 --> 00:20:54,173
I...

214
00:20:55,863 --> 00:20:57,333
just miss Singkhon.

215
00:21:06,673 --> 00:21:08,293
I also dreamed of him last night.

216
00:21:18,453 --> 00:21:19,773
Do you remember...

217
00:21:20,933 --> 00:21:22,413
how much Singkhon

218
00:21:22,853 --> 00:21:24,733
cherished Khao Luang forest

219
00:21:24,933 --> 00:21:27,013
and Tambralinga?

220
00:21:28,433 --> 00:21:29,433
I do.

221
00:21:31,393 --> 00:21:33,173
He never wanted anyone to invade

222
00:21:33,413 --> 00:21:34,473
or ruin it.

223
00:21:35,253 --> 00:21:36,293
If you know that...

224
00:21:36,333 --> 00:21:38,533
But Tambralinga means a lot to me,

225
00:21:38,573 --> 00:21:39,773
Thara...

226
00:21:42,173 --> 00:21:43,453
and Siwat as well.

227
00:21:49,653 --> 00:21:51,173
No matter what happens,

228
00:21:52,933 --> 00:21:54,853
I'll face the consequences.

229
00:21:58,253 --> 00:21:59,633
Please don't stop us.

230
00:22:38,833 --> 00:22:39,733
Aunt Kate,

231
00:22:41,993 --> 00:22:43,933
may I speak with you?

232
00:22:45,833 --> 00:22:46,693
Have a seat.

233
00:23:02,453 --> 00:23:03,293
Thank you.

234
00:23:09,933 --> 00:23:10,933
I love this place.

235
00:23:13,413 --> 00:23:15,933
I wanna stay here
with Khunkhao, Thara, and you.

236
00:23:17,513 --> 00:23:20,733
I know no one can ever forget
the pain of losing their parents.

237
00:23:27,813 --> 00:23:29,013
I just can't do anything.

238
00:23:31,753 --> 00:23:33,270
Unable to change the past...

239
00:23:36,933 --> 00:23:38,273
And unable to move forward.

240
00:23:42,853 --> 00:23:44,773
Why did my father hurt Uncle Singkhon?

241
00:23:47,053 --> 00:23:49,373
I want to know what exactly happened.

242
00:23:54,413 --> 00:23:56,413
There's someone who knows that very well.

243
00:24:35,573 --> 00:24:36,573
I'm here.

244
00:24:39,653 --> 00:24:41,653
I'm not getting out until I see you.

245
00:24:42,693 --> 00:24:43,693
I'm right here.

246
00:24:50,853 --> 00:24:51,693
Aisoon?

247
00:24:55,093 --> 00:24:56,013
I'm sorry.

248
00:24:57,373 --> 00:25:00,173
He wouldn't show himself
if I didn't bring you with me.

249
00:25:01,373 --> 00:25:02,813
As soon as I get out of the car,

250
00:25:03,733 --> 00:25:05,213
drive away immediately.

251
00:25:05,253 --> 00:25:06,413
But what about you?

252
00:25:06,773 --> 00:25:08,173
Just go. Don't worry about me.

253
00:25:37,633 --> 00:25:39,053
Where are the Shiva lingam
and the Yoni stone?

254
00:25:57,333 --> 00:25:58,173
Aunt Kate!

255
00:26:02,813 --> 00:26:03,613
Aunt Kate!

256
00:26:04,173 --> 00:26:05,013
Siwat...

257
00:26:05,773 --> 00:26:06,773
Come closer and you'll die.

258
00:26:11,933 --> 00:26:12,653
Aunt Kate...

259
00:26:12,733 --> 00:26:13,533
Aunt Kate!

260
00:26:19,533 --> 00:26:20,653
Have you seen my mom?

261
00:26:21,333 --> 00:26:22,133
No, bro.

262
00:26:24,853 --> 00:26:26,491
Mind, have you seen my mom?

263
00:26:27,933 --> 00:26:28,693
No.

264
00:26:29,293 --> 00:26:30,453
Where could she be?

265
00:26:31,013 --> 00:26:31,933
Her phone's off.

266
00:26:31,973 --> 00:26:32,773
Lookwaii,

267
00:26:32,973 --> 00:26:33,893
have you seen Siwat?

268
00:26:34,373 --> 00:26:36,013
He's not home and won't pick up my calls.

269
00:26:36,893 --> 00:26:38,093
- No.
- Wait.

270
00:26:38,893 --> 00:26:42,453
Are you not gonna tell us
about the powers Siwat possesses?

271
00:26:53,453 --> 00:26:54,253
Khun,

272
00:26:54,293 --> 00:26:56,133
someone just sent a picture to our page.

273
00:26:59,413 --> 00:27:00,173
Hey...

274
00:27:03,333 --> 00:27:04,453
That's Aisoon,

275
00:27:04,753 --> 00:27:05,653
one of Michael's people.

276
00:27:06,173 --> 00:27:07,693
With my mom and Siwat.

277
00:27:10,073 --> 00:27:11,142
What's going on?

278
00:27:17,613 --> 00:27:19,813
How much longer
will you keep hunting me down?

279
00:27:20,453 --> 00:27:22,133
Until the day you die.

280
00:27:29,213 --> 00:27:30,013
Maria?

281
00:27:31,673 --> 00:27:32,835
Get rid of him.

