289
00:28:12,053 --> 00:28:13,173
We have her.

290
00:28:13,413 --> 00:28:14,693
We'll keep her as our bargaining chip.

291
00:28:15,553 --> 00:28:17,020
Siwat has his powers.

292
00:28:17,413 --> 00:28:18,813
Do you wanna be burned alive?

293
00:28:24,393 --> 00:28:26,333
I'll take you to someone...

294
00:28:26,373 --> 00:28:29,413
