297
00:28:56,613 --> 00:28:57,813
No, Dad...

298
00:28:57,973 --> 00:28:58,813
Kill him!

299
00:29:02,173 --> 00:29:02,973
Dean...

300
00:29:03,533 --> 00:29:04,253
