303
00:29:12,533 --> 00:29:13,453
Do it!

304
00:29:13,573 --> 00:29:14,493
Shoot me!

305
00:29:14,733 --> 00:29:15,533
Sure!

306
00:29:15,806 --> 00:29:17,086
I'm fine with that!

307
00:29:17,453 --> 00:29:19,573
You asked for it,
so I'll make sure you get it.

308
00:29:19,613 --> 00:29:20,333
Dean...

309
00:29:27,133 --> 00:29:27,853
Hey!

310
00:29:42,373 --> 00:29:43,653
How did you get here?

311
00:29:44,013 --> 00:29:45,013
Thanks, Dean.

312
00:29:52,293 --> 00:29:53,159
Aisoon,

313
00:29:53,613 --> 00:29:56,253
