319
00:30:08,173 --> 00:30:09,573
The one who did it...

320
00:30:12,173 --> 00:30:13,093
was her.

321
00:30:18,173 --> 00:30:19,053
Liar!

322
00:30:19,973 --> 00:30:21,773
My mom would never drug Khun.

323
00:30:22,293 --> 00:30:23,213
You're lying!

324
00:30:23,773 --> 00:30:25,693
Your mom drugged Khunkhao

325
00:30:26,713 --> 00:30:28,133
so I could get the Shiva lingam.

326
00:30:29,773 --> 00:30:31,173
And Singkhon had to die...

327
00:30:31,653 --> 00:30:32,853
because...

328
00:30:33,593 --> 00:30:35,253
he was betrayed by his own sister.

329
00:30:36,013 --> 00:30:36,853
That's not true.

330
00:30:37,333 --> 00:30:38,653
Mom, tell us he's lying!

331
00:30:39,133 --> 00:30:41,173
You didn't betray Uncle Singkhon,
did you?

332
00:30:52,773 --> 00:30:53,892
I'm sorry.

333
00:31:09,293 --> 00:31:10,093
Dad!

334
00:31:10,413 --> 00:31:11,413
They're running away!

335
00:31:55,073 --> 00:31:57,133
If you'd been honest with my dad,

336
00:31:57,333 --> 00:31:58,570
he wouldn't have had to die.

337
00:31:58,773 --> 00:32:00,213
I'm really sorry, Khunkhao.

338
00:32:03,493 --> 00:32:04,333
Khun...

339
00:32:04,911 --> 00:32:09,271
♫No matter how long it takes♫

340
00:32:09,311 --> 00:32:11,911
♫I'll still choose to love you♫

341
00:32:18,071 --> 00:32:19,471
