342
00:32:20,531 --> 00:32:21,871
Tell me the truth.

343
00:32:22,551 --> 00:32:24,071
Tell everyone

344
00:32:25,111 --> 00:32:27,191
what really happened.

345
00:32:29,991 --> 00:32:31,591
Searching for Tambralinga...

346
00:32:33,911 --> 00:32:36,212
has always been Singkhon's dream.

347
00:32:39,311 --> 00:32:41,252
A check for five million baht will be yours...

348
00:32:41,261 --> 00:32:42,031
[Singkhon Sriwichit]

349
00:32:42,041 --> 00:32:43,911
if you agree to work with me.

350
00:32:46,951 --> 00:32:48,271
We needed the money

351
00:32:48,311 --> 00:32:50,751
for Thara's heart surgery,

352
00:32:51,511 --> 00:32:52,914
so he said yes.

353
00:32:53,951 --> 00:32:54,845
Fine.

354
00:32:55,136 --> 00:32:56,071
I'll do it.

355
00:32:57,631 --> 00:32:59,151
But I have one condition.

356
00:33:00,311 --> 00:33:01,991
Once we discover the ruins of Tambralinga,

357
00:33:02,451 --> 00:33:04,391
we must absolutely keep the location secret

358
00:33:04,911 --> 00:33:07,111
until I decide the time's right.

359
00:33:07,931 --> 00:33:09,911
I won't allow Khao Luang forest
to be destroyed,

360
00:33:10,991 --> 00:33:12,831
not by those treasure hunters.

361
00:33:13,651 --> 00:33:14,651
Deal.

362
00:33:14,791 --> 00:33:18,551
Finding Tambralinga
has always been my dream, too.

363
00:33:19,851 --> 00:33:22,191
I don't want the forest
to be destroyed, either.

364
00:33:43,271 --> 00:33:46,311
After years of searching Khao Luang forest,

365
00:33:46,897 --> 00:33:48,391
Aisoon discovered something.

366
00:33:48,431 --> 00:33:51,671
He realized that the Yoni stone
Michael obtained when he adopted Siwat,

367
00:33:51,951 --> 00:33:53,951
and Khunkhao's Shiva lingam,

368
00:33:54,391 --> 00:33:56,111
were connected to Tambralinga.

369
00:33:56,971 --> 00:33:58,791
We set out immediately.

370
00:34:34,151 --> 00:34:35,071
I'm okay.

371
00:34:35,711 --> 00:34:36,711
Don't worry.

372
00:35:06,751 --> 00:35:07,871
Please take some medicine.

373
00:35:28,191 --> 00:35:29,191
Thanks.

374
00:35:42,471 --> 00:35:43,471
How's he doing?

375
00:35:46,971 --> 00:35:47,971
Not good.

376
00:35:50,151 --> 00:35:51,391
We can only ease the pain.

377
00:35:54,631 --> 00:35:56,031
But not long after entering the forest,

378
00:35:56,451 --> 00:35:58,231
Michael contracted cerebral malaria

379
00:35:58,271 --> 00:35:59,831
and had to return to the UK for treatment.

380
00:35:59,871 --> 00:36:01,191
He never came back.

381
00:36:02,311 --> 00:36:05,991
But Aisoon did,
a day before Thara's surgery.

382
00:36:13,311 --> 00:36:14,111
Thara!

383
00:36:14,311 --> 00:36:14,991
Mom!

384
00:36:15,031 --> 00:36:15,871
Mom!

385
00:36:16,951 --> 00:36:17,930
Are you sure?

386
00:36:21,831 --> 00:36:22,951
If you fight me,

387
00:36:23,751 --> 00:36:24,591
your son dies.

388
00:36:25,551 --> 00:36:26,431
Let me go!

389
00:36:27,711 --> 00:36:28,711
Mom!

390
00:36:33,311 --> 00:36:34,151
Mom...

391
00:36:35,551 --> 00:36:37,231
Don't you ever hurt Thara!

392
00:36:43,111 --> 00:36:43,991
Here, Khun.

393
00:36:44,591 --> 00:36:45,711
Have some hot cocoa.

394
00:36:46,311 --> 00:36:47,591
Thank you, Aunt Kate.

395
00:36:52,311 --> 00:36:55,471
He forced me to drug Khunkhao

396
00:36:55,791 --> 00:36:57,871
so he could steal the Shiva lingam.

397
00:37:07,711 --> 00:37:08,591
Khun...

398
00:37:11,271 --> 00:37:12,311
How do you feel, Khun?

399
00:37:16,551 --> 00:37:18,511
You're just very sleepy, aren't you?

400
00:37:19,471 --> 00:37:20,371
Yes.

401
00:37:24,231 --> 00:37:25,095
Khun,

402
00:37:25,631 --> 00:37:27,031
just take a nap right here.

403
00:37:27,311 --> 00:37:29,951
I'll check if Singkhon's ready.

404
00:38:00,031 --> 00:38:00,871
No!

405
00:38:01,311 --> 00:38:02,071
No...

406
00:38:03,231 --> 00:38:04,111
No!

407
00:38:04,811 --> 00:38:05,671
No...

408
00:38:08,511 --> 00:38:09,351
No!

409
00:38:09,551 --> 00:38:11,191
Give me back my necklace.

410
00:38:16,691 --> 00:38:18,751
Once Aisoon had the necklace,

411
00:38:18,791 --> 00:38:20,671
he wouldn't let Thara go.

412
00:38:21,491 --> 00:38:22,671
In the end,

413
00:38:22,711 --> 00:38:24,711
I had to tell Singkhon the truth.

414
00:38:25,631 --> 00:38:28,191
We hunted him down in Khao Luang forest

415
00:38:28,231 --> 00:38:29,911
to save Thara.

416
00:38:31,911 --> 00:38:33,031
Where's Thara?!

417
00:38:33,471 --> 00:38:34,911
Answer me!

418
00:38:39,431 --> 00:38:40,151
Watch out!

419
00:38:42,871 --> 00:38:43,871
Singkhon...

420
00:38:46,991 --> 00:38:47,821
Watch out!

421
00:38:58,351 --> 00:38:59,311
Singkhon!

422
00:39:04,591 --> 00:39:06,031
Singkhon!!

423
00:39:06,511 --> 00:39:08,091
Singkhon!!

424
00:39:12,391 --> 00:39:13,631
Singkhon...

425
00:39:18,551 --> 00:39:19,311
Mom!

426
00:39:19,671 --> 00:39:20,471
Thara?!

427
00:39:33,071 --> 00:39:34,991
After Singkhon died,

428
00:39:38,871 --> 00:39:40,392
when I found Thara...

429
00:39:42,111 --> 00:39:43,871
he was nearly dead too.

430
00:39:46,791 --> 00:39:47,711
But...

431
00:39:48,364 --> 00:39:52,311
why didn't my father know that
Aisoon took Uncle Singkhon's life?

432
00:39:53,351 --> 00:39:54,991
I was ashamed,

433
00:39:55,231 --> 00:39:57,751
so I didn't let anyone know.

434
00:39:58,791 --> 00:40:01,991
I never thought Aisoon
would dare work for Michael again.

435
00:40:06,471 --> 00:40:08,031
Before Michael passed away,

436
00:40:09,331 --> 00:40:12,311
he asked me
to take him to look for the city again.

437
00:40:14,311 --> 00:40:16,391
He wanted to help you, Siwat.

438
00:40:18,311 --> 00:40:20,610
If you'd been honest with my dad,

439
00:40:22,371 --> 00:40:23,631
he wouldn't have had to die.

440
00:40:25,051 --> 00:40:26,191
I was scared.

441
00:40:27,691 --> 00:40:29,351
Too afraid to risk it.

442
00:40:34,871 --> 00:40:36,711
I'm really sorry, Khunkhao.

443
00:40:43,021 --> 00:40:44,118
Khun...

444
00:41:05,231 --> 00:41:06,231
Professor!

445
00:41:06,551 --> 00:41:09,111
Fetch me the Shiva lingam and the Yoni stone!

446
00:41:12,206 --> 00:41:16,726
♫No matter how long it takes♫

447
00:41:16,766 --> 00:41:19,366
♫I'll still choose to love you♫

448
00:41:27,086 --> 00:41:28,726
You guys suck.

449
00:41:30,606 --> 00:41:31,846
You too.

450
00:41:32,006 --> 00:41:33,606
Got the nerve to crawl back, huh?

451
00:41:39,706 --> 00:41:40,966
Thanks to your son,

452
00:41:41,626 --> 00:41:43,126
everything's f*cked up.

453
00:41:43,326 --> 00:41:44,386
No Shiva lingam.

454
00:41:44,426 --> 00:41:45,526
Nothing at all.

455
00:41:47,126 --> 00:41:48,526
There's still a chance.

456
00:41:49,686 --> 00:41:51,286
After all the times you've messed up,

457
00:41:51,326 --> 00:41:52,606
you've got countless chances, huh?

458
00:41:52,806 --> 00:41:54,686
Come on. Without me,

459
00:41:55,526 --> 00:41:57,766
you'll never get the Heart of the Vedas,

460
00:41:58,166 --> 00:42:00,206
that priceless gem
that could make you crazy rich.

461
00:42:01,126 --> 00:42:01,886
And?

462
00:42:01,926 --> 00:42:03,166
I haven't even gotten it yet.

463
00:42:03,246 --> 00:42:04,246
Who's to blame?

464
00:42:04,786 --> 00:42:05,486
Well,

465
00:42:05,966 --> 00:42:06,886
then kill me.

466
00:42:08,886 --> 00:42:09,766
Sure.

467
00:42:10,006 --> 00:42:11,006
As you wish.

468
00:42:11,126 --> 00:42:11,926
Yeah.

469
00:42:12,466 --> 00:42:13,406
Go ahead and kill me,

470
00:42:13,926 --> 00:42:16,846
then go back to being
an invisible MILF model

471
00:42:17,386 --> 00:42:19,243
with no Michael's money backing you up.

472
00:42:21,366 --> 00:42:22,366
Kill me.

473
00:42:23,406 --> 00:42:24,846
Don't you dare try me.

474
00:42:28,446 --> 00:42:29,446
Maybe...

475
00:42:29,726 --> 00:42:32,040
you have to choose between killing me

476
00:42:32,646 --> 00:42:33,926
or walking forward with me.

477
00:42:37,246 --> 00:42:38,686
So, what's your plan?

478
00:42:41,766 --> 00:42:43,486
They've got both stones,

479
00:42:44,686 --> 00:42:46,886
and Siwat will surely go after the city.

480
00:42:46,926 --> 00:42:48,246
We just need to ambush them.

481
00:42:50,406 --> 00:42:52,806
After all those years following Michael,

482
00:42:52,846 --> 00:42:55,206
you still haven't laid eyes on the ruins.

483
00:42:55,359 --> 00:42:56,519
But someone has,

484
00:42:56,966 --> 00:42:57,606
you know?

485
00:42:57,646 --> 00:42:58,926
And he knows where it is.

486
00:43:04,726 --> 00:43:07,046
That Professor Thakoon or something?

487
00:43:10,086 --> 00:43:13,046
He's as obsessed with Tambralinga as Michael.

488
00:43:13,886 --> 00:43:16,406
He even visited the city ruins in the forest
with Singkhon

489
00:43:16,526 --> 00:43:18,846
and tried to document it in a book,

490
00:43:19,346 --> 00:43:22,126
insisting to the scholars
that the city was real.

491
00:43:22,486 --> 00:43:23,806
But no one believed him.

492
00:43:24,373 --> 00:43:27,253
Then he became known as a mad scholar.

493
00:43:30,386 --> 00:43:33,846
Are you sure
he's gonna lead us to the city?

494
00:44:13,706 --> 00:44:14,566
Professor!

495
00:44:39,366 --> 00:44:40,686
Brahmin Kalakal...

496
00:44:42,806 --> 00:44:44,966
I've long awaited
the moment I could stand before you.

497
00:44:46,486 --> 00:44:48,366
What is it that you desire from me?

498
00:44:50,046 --> 00:44:53,006
I wish to serve you loyally, Brahmin Kalakal,

499
00:44:54,046 --> 00:44:56,406
the Earth Bender of Tambralinga.

500
00:44:57,846 --> 00:44:59,166
Whatever you ask,

501
00:45:00,266 --> 00:45:01,806
I will obey.

502
00:45:03,686 --> 00:45:06,366
Bring me Suriya and the others.

503
00:45:07,906 --> 00:45:10,326
You may now enter my body,

504
00:45:12,366 --> 00:45:14,006
and I shall handle it myself.

505
00:45:26,406 --> 00:45:27,286
This is crazy!

506
00:45:27,566 --> 00:45:28,446
My goodness!

507
00:45:29,126 --> 00:45:30,326
He's gone crazy!

508
00:45:31,926 --> 00:45:32,711
Khun...

509
00:45:36,366 --> 00:45:38,286
Khun must not know about this.

510
00:45:38,846 --> 00:45:39,766
Professor...

511
00:45:44,246 --> 00:45:45,246
Professor!

512
00:45:46,526 --> 00:45:47,406
Professor...

513
00:45:47,446 --> 00:45:50,046
Fetch me the Shiva lingam and the Yoni stone!

514
00:45:51,646 --> 00:45:52,286
Professor...

515
00:46:10,526 --> 00:46:11,686
Who the hell are you?

516
00:46:12,566 --> 00:46:15,022
If you want the Shiva lingam
and the Yoni stone,

517
00:46:15,406 --> 00:46:16,686
I can get them for you.

518
00:46:19,086 --> 00:46:20,526
We truly can.

519
00:46:21,166 --> 00:46:22,766
You're their enemies, aren't you?

520
00:46:23,686 --> 00:46:24,966
But in exchange,

521
00:46:25,806 --> 00:46:28,246
you must take us to Tambralinga with you.

522
00:46:30,806 --> 00:46:32,356
Show me...

523
00:46:34,086 --> 00:46:37,046
how you're gonna obtain both of the stones.

524
00:46:43,446 --> 00:46:44,646
I've got a plan.

525
00:46:59,526 --> 00:47:01,206
If they know we're the Benders,

526
00:47:01,246 --> 00:47:02,726
then what's their plan?

527
00:47:02,886 --> 00:47:04,046
We can't avoid it.

528
00:47:04,206 --> 00:47:05,726
Then we must face it.

529
00:47:05,767 --> 00:47:06,447
Hey!

530
00:47:07,246 --> 00:47:07,966
Wait...

531
00:47:12,206 --> 00:47:15,046
Everything must return to the beginning.

532
00:47:15,406 --> 00:47:16,486
The beginning?

533
00:47:16,686 --> 00:47:19,006
It's pathetic
seeing you all protecting each other.

534
00:47:19,046 --> 00:47:21,606
No matter how hard you try to lie to us,

535
00:47:21,806 --> 00:47:22,966
I won't buy it.

536
00:47:23,006 --> 00:47:25,006
Guess you'll have to see for yourselves.

537
00:47:25,246 --> 00:47:29,486
(Incanting)

538
00:47:29,526 --> 00:47:33,966
♫No matter how long it takes♫

539
00:47:34,006 --> 00:47:37,446
♫I'll still choose to love you♫

540
00:47:37,486 --> 00:47:44,686
♫This heart's forever loyal, no difference♫

541
00:47:45,486 --> 00:47:48,926
♫It keeps beating for you forevermore♫

542
00:47:48,966 --> 00:47:52,526
♫Never want to change, alright♫

543
00:47:52,566 --> 00:47:57,406
♫There's only you there inside my heart♫

544
00:47:57,446 --> 00:48:02,046
♫My love for you never evanesces♫
